{"tid":558630,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"吸二手嘅大麻煙會唔會stone到？","createTime":"2018-02-12T12:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T07:54:04.000Z","uid":140879,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6cc1e231f70f65624ee42d2d2fd7389bc881a422","tid":558630,"uid":140879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T12:16:28.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟係溫哥華生活。有次屎忽痕走堂去咗夜遊一條最多hobo嘅街，基本上每人都食緊，痴撚晒線咁。<br />\n咁我沿途一直吸鳩晒d 二手大麻煙，到最後行返去冇hobo 嘅街，全身都飄到企唔穩，有少少似醉但係更加wing 。<br />\n其實我係心理作用定二手真係都會有effect 呢？<br />\n<br />\n利申：飲啤酒一罐就面紅，6罐來必醉。"},{"pid":"d86f00a146ae8e7e0ede9d80f852e2570e1d698c","tid":558630,"uid":140879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T12:18:50.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"85ee7e5efd9c3e804682a0a636670a82504621c8","tid":558630,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T12:19:27.000Z","msg":"吸夠咪會"},{"pid":"fad0c8be1bb46d828bf821979a9e7805662e002a","tid":558630,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T12:19:55.000Z","msg":"當佢裝香咁燒，咁全屋都好開心"},{"pid":"3aae2763f0e06bceac716618cdf3c770c3e73eac","tid":558630,"uid":170974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T12:51:59.000Z","msg":"會 但當街當行 溫哥華空氣又流通人又多極有限 咁易stone 啲人就唔洗困自己入車玩hotbox"},{"pid":"a0628d9b0d714699276f9ef4f007d55d5142e43e","tid":558630,"uid":140879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aae2763f0e06bceac716618cdf3c770c3e73eac","tid":558630,"uid":170974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T12:51:59.000Z","msg":"會 但當街當行 溫哥華空氣又流通人又多極有限 咁易stone 啲人就唔洗困自己入車玩hotbox"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T13:06:42.000Z","msg":"條街煙霧彌漫"},{"pid":"d3eb6f388f6bb7b442dcb9b618c7ff8ccfdfb186","tid":558630,"uid":18479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T13:16:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/91172/印尼警方燒3-3噸大麻%E3%80%80high爆全鎮/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F911